#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about calm consequences.\n"
"\n"
"Our actions have consequences. Some consequences happen naturally (“if you break something, you can’t use it anymore”). Other consequences we set as a family to motivate us to follow the rules (“if you come home late, you can’t go out with friends tomorrow”).\n"
"\n"
"HOW you set and use consequences together matters.\n"
"\n"
"Getting consequences right helps teens behave better and makes family life calmer."
msgstr ""
"Mada ya leo ni kuhusu athari nyepesi.\n"
"\n"
"Matendo yetu yana matokeo. Baadhi ya matokeo hutokea kwa kawaida (“ kama ukivunja kitu, huwezi kukitumia tena”). Adhabu nyepesi zingine tunaweka kama familia ili kutuhamasisha kufuata sheria (“ kama ukirudi nyumbani ukiwa umechelewa, hautaruhusiwa kutoka na marafiki kesho”).\n"
"\n"
"JINSI unavyoweka na kutumia adhabu nyepesi pamoja ni muhimu.\n"
"Kuweka matokeo ipasavyo husaidia vijana kuenenda vyema na hufanya maisha ya familia kuwa na utulivu zaidi.\n"
"Mada ya leo ni kuhusu athari nyepesi.\n"
"\n"
"Matendo yetu yana matokeo. Baadhi ya matokeo hutokea kwa kawaida (“ kama ukivunja kitu, huwezi kukitumia tena”). Adhabu nyepesi zingine tunaweka kama familia ili kutuhamasisha kufuata sheria (“ kama ukirudi nyumbani ukiwa umechelewa, hautaruhusiwa kutoka na marafiki kesho”)."

